generations.noise_image_prompt: Design a cybernetic-enhanced Ape character sitting in a high-tech control room surrounded by holographic screens displaying complex AI algorithms and futuristic data. The Ape should have a focused expression, wearing sleek cybernetic glasses, and typing rapidly on a holographic keyboard. The color scheme should include neon blues, purples, and greens to convey a futuristic atmosphere. Incorporate elements like glowing circuit patterns on the Ape's skin and robotic enhancements to highlight their tech-savvy persona and analytical nature. Emphasize the Ape's innovative mindset and problem-solving skills in the cyberpunk-inspired design.
